le-[1.03] active:scale-[0.98] group">Vypočúvaj ukážky<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-right size-4 ml-2 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg></button><button data-slot="button" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap font-medium disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg:not([class*=&#x27;size-&#x27;])]:size-4 shrink-0 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 outline-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-ring/50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 aria-invalid:border-destructive border bg-background shadow-xs dark:bg-input/30 dark:border-input dark:hover:bg-input/50 h-10 has-[&gt;svg]:px-4 border-white/[0.08] text-foreground/80 hover:bg-white/[0.06] hover:text-foreground hover:border-white/15 px-8 sm:px-10 py-5 sm:py-6 text-base rounded-xl backdrop-blur-md transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.03] active:scale-[0.98] group">Konfigurovať môj originál<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-settings size-4 ml-2 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:rotate-90" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9.671 4.136a2.34 2.34 0 0 1 4.659 0 2.34 2.34 0 0 0 3.319 1.915 2.34 2.34 0 0 1 2.33 4.033 2.34 2.34 0 0 0 0 3.831 2.34 2.34 0 0 1-2.33 4.033 2.34 2.34 0 0 0-3.319 1.915 2.34 2.34 0 0 1-4.659 0 2.34 2.34 0 0 0-3.32-1.915 2.34 2.34 0 0 1-2.33-4.033 2.34 2.34 0 0 0 0-3.831A2.34 2.34 0 0 1 6.35 6.051a2.34 2.34 0 0 0 3.319-1.915"></path><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"></circle></svg></button></div></div><div class="absolute bottom-6 sm:bottom-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 z-10 hero-fade-item" style="animation-delay:1.5s"><button class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2 group cursor-pointer" aria-label="Scroll down"><span class="text-[10px] text-muted-foreground/30 uppercase tracking-[0.25em] group-hover:text-muted-foreground/50 transition-colors duration-300">Scroll</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down size-4 text-muted-foreground/25 bounce-chevron" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></button></div></section><div class="section-divider"></div><section class="py-16 sm:py-24 lg:py-28 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="relative overflow-hidden"><img src="/aluplex/aluplex-138.jpg" alt="" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-[0.06] grayscale mix-blend-luminosity pointer-events-none" loading="lazy" aria-hidden="true"/><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#0a0a0a]/95 pointer-events-none"></div><div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto"><div class="text-center mb-10 sm:mb-14 fade-in-up"><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-4"><div class="w-8 h-[2px] bg-primary"></div><span class="text-xs font-semibold text-primary uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Čo nás odlišuje</span><div class="w-8 h-[2px] bg-primary"></div></div></div><div class="grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-3 sm:gap-4 lg:gap-6"><div class="fade-in-up group bg-card/50 border border-[#2a2a2a]/60 rounded-2xl p-5 sm:p-6 lg:p-8 text-center card-hover backdrop-blur-sm" style="transition-delay:0ms"><div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 rounded-2xl bg-primary/10 group-hover:bg-primary/20 transition-colors duration-300 mb-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-heart size-5 sm:size-6 text-primary" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2 9.5a5.5 5.5 0 0 1 9.591-3.676.56.56 0 0 0 .818 0A5.49 5.49 0 0 1 22 9.5c0 2.29-1.5 4-3 5.5l-5.492 5.313a2 2 0 0 1-3 .019L5 15c-1.5-1.5-3-3.2-3-5.5"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Ručná výroba</h3><p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">Žiadna montážna linka. Žiadne skratky. Každý ALUPLEXamp sa rodí na pracovnom stole — spojka za spojkou, hodiny precíznej práce, ktorú pocítite v každej vibrácii a každom harmonickom.</p></div><div class="fade-in-up group bg-card/50 border border-[#2a2a2a]/60 rounded-2xl p-5 sm:p-6 lg:p-8 text-center card-hover backdrop-blur-sm" style="transition-delay:100ms"><div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 rounded-2xl bg-primary/10 group-hover:bg-primary/20 transition-colors duration-300 mb-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-target size-5 sm:size-6 text-primary" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"></circle><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"></circle></svg></div><h3 class="text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Turret Board</h3><p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">Tak to robili majstri v šesťdesiatych — čistý, priamy signálový path bez nežiaducich priesečníkov. Žiadny PCB. Žiadne kompromisy. Iba drôt, kov a svit vákuových lamp.</p></div><div class="fade-in-up group bg-card/50 border border-[#2a2a2a]/60 rounded-2xl p-5 sm:p-6 lg:p-8 text-center card-hover backdrop-blur-sm" style="transition-delay:200ms"><div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 rounded-2xl bg-primary/10 group-hover:bg-primary/20 transition-colors duration-300 mb-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-shield size-5 sm:size-6 text-primary" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z"></path></svg></div><h3 class="text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Prémiové komponenty</h3><p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">Každý kondenzátor, transformátor a odpor je vybraný na základe sluchu — nie podľa katalógu. Sme ľudia, ktorí počujú, a stavame pre tých, ktorí počujú.</p></div><div class="fade-in-up group bg-card/50 border border-[#2a2a2a]/60 rounded-2xl p-5 sm:p-6 lg:p-8 text-center card-hover backdrop-blur-sm" style="transition-delay:300ms"><div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 rounded-2xl bg-primary/10 group-hover:bg-primary/20 transition-colors duration-300 mb-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-music size-5 sm:size-6 text-primary" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 18V5l12-2v13"></path><circle cx="6" cy="18" r="3"></circle><circle cx="18" cy="16" r="3"></circle></svg></div><h3 class="text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Organický zvuk</h3><p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">Tento aparat dýcha. Reaguje na váš najjemnejší náklon prstov i najťažší úder plektra — od šepotu až po kričanie, od medového cleanu po krémový overdrive, ktorý sa len tak neprestáva spievať.</p></div></div></div></div></section><div class="section-divider"></div><section id="specs" class="py-16 sm:py-24 lg:py-28 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto"><div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-start"><div><div class="fade-in-up"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4"><div class="w-8 h-[2px] bg-primary"></div><span class="text-xs font-semibold text-primary uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Čo je vnútri</span></div><h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-foreground mb-6 leading-tight">Hliník. Remeslo. Výkon.</h2><p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-8 text-sm sm:text-base max-w-xl">Predstavte si podvozok, ktorý sa pod vašimi rukami zahrieva na presne tú správnu teplotu — nie horúci, nie studený, ale živý. Hliník je chrbtica ALUPLEXampu: chladí lampy tichou, prírodnou eleganciou, nikdy nezasahuje do vášho signálu a s plynúcimi rokmi získa patinu, ktorá rozpráva príbeh vašich hudobných ciest.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 sm:gap-4"><div class="fade-in-up group bg-card/50 border border-[#2a2a2a]/60 rounded-2xl p-4 sm:p-5 card-hover backdrop-blur-sm" style="transition-delay:100ms"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3"><div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 group-hover:bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center transition-colors"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thermometer-sun size-4 text-primary" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2v2"></path><path d="M12 8a4 4 0 0 0-1.645 7.647"></path><path d="M2 12h2"></path><path d="M20 14.54a4 4 0 1 1-4 0V4a2 2 0 0 1 4 0z"></path><path d="m4.93 4.93 1.41 1.41"></path><path d="m6.34 17.66-1.41 1.41"></path></svg></div><h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-foreground">Odvod tepla</h4></div><p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">Celý podvozok funguje ako pasívny chladič — žiadne ventilátory, žiadny elektronický šum, iba kov, ktorý jemne vedie teplo preč od vákuových lamp a necháva ich dýchať v pokoji.</p></div><div class="fade-in-up group bg-card/50 border border-[#2a2a2a]/60 rounded-2xl p-4 sm:p-5 card-hover backdrop-blur-sm" style="transition-delay:200ms"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3"><div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 group-hover:bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center transition-colors"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-weight size-4 text-primary" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="5" r="3"></circle><path d="M6.5 8a2 2 0 0 0-1.905 1.46L2.1 18.5A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.925-2.54L19.4 9.5A2 2 0 0 0 17.48 8Z"></path></svg></div><h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-foreground">Nízka hmotnosť</h4></div><p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">12,5 kg čistého zvuku. Hliník odstraňuje bremeno, ktoré ste nikdy nechceli niesť — a zanecháva len to, na čom záleží: lásku k hudbe a slobodu pohybu.</p></div><div class="fade-in-up group bg-card/50 border border-[#2a2a2a]/60 rounded-2xl p-4 sm:p-5 card-hover backdrop-blur-sm" style="transition-delay:300ms"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3"><div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 group-hover:bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center transition-colors"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-magnet size-4 text-primary" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m12 15 4 4"></path><path d="M2.352 10.648a1.205 1.205 0 0 0 0 1.704l2.296 2.296a1.205 1.205 0 0 0 1.704 0l6.029-6.029a1 1 0 1 1 3 3l-6.029 6.029a1.205 1.205 0 0 0 0 1.704l2.296 2.296a1.205 1.205 0 0 0 1.704 0l6.365-6.367A1 1 0 0 0 8.716 4.282z"></path><path d="m5 8 4 4"></path></svg></div><h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-foreground">Nemagnetický</h4></div><p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">Hliník je nemagnetický — váš podvozok nikdy nezasahuje do snímačov gitary. Každý nádych, každý harmonický putuje od vašich prstov k lampám nepoškvrnený a slobodný.</p></div><div class="fade-in-up group bg-card/50 border border-[#2a2a2a]/60 rounded-2xl p-4 sm:p-5 card-hover backdrop-blur-sm" style="transition-delay:400ms"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3"><div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 group-hover:bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center transition-colors"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-shield-check size-4 text-primary" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z"></path><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"></path></svg></div><h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-foreground">Odolnosť voči korózii</h4></div><p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">Prírodná oxidácia hliníka vytvára ochranný štít — aparat nepodlieha hrdze, ale starnie s tichou krásou patiny, ktorá rozpráva príbeh každého vystúpenia a každej nočnej session.</p></div></div></div><div class="fade-in-up" style="transition-delay:200ms"><div class="relative bg-card/50 border border-[#2a2a2a]/60 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden tube-glow backdrop-blur-sm"><div class="relative"><img src="/aluplex/aluplex-back-naked.jpg" alt="ALUPLEXamp chassis internals" class="w-full h-auto object-cover"/><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-card via-transparent to-transparent"></div></div><div class="p-6 sm:p-8 lg:p-10 relative"><div class="text-center mb-8"><p class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-3">Hmotnosť</p><div class="text-6xl sm:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-bold text-gradient-amber leading-none">12.5</div><p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-muted-foreground mt-2 font-light">kg</p></div><div class="bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/[0.06] rounded-2xl p-4 mb-6"><div class="flex items-center gap-3"><div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-power size-5 text-primary" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2v10"></path><path d="M18.4 6.6a9 9 0 1 1-12.77.04"></path></svg></div><span class="text-xs sm:text-sm font-semibold text-foreground uppercase tracking-wider">Vstavaný prepínač napätia: 115V / 230V</span></div></div><div class="text-center pt-6 border-t border-white/[0.06]"><p class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs font-mono text-muted-foreground/40 tracking-[0.4em] uppercase">HLINÍKOVÝ PODVOZOK</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><div class="section-divider"></div><section class="py-16 sm:py-24 lg:py-28 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto"><div class="text-center mb-12 sm:mb-16 fade-in-up"><h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">Architektúra zvuku</h2><p class="text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto text-sm sm:text-base">Parametre sú len čísla na papieri. Skutočná história sa odohráva vo vnútri — v horúcich vákuových lampách, v medených drôtoch, v tóne, ktorý dýcha a žije s každou vašou notou.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-3 sm:gap-4 lg:gap-6 mb-10 sm:mb-14"><div class="fade-in-up group bg-card/50 border border-[#2a2a2a]/60 rounded-2xl p-4 sm:p-5 lg:p-8 text-center card-hover backdrop-blur-sm" style="transition-delay:0ms"><div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 rounded-2xl bg-primary/10 group-hover:bg-primary/20 transition-colors duration-300 mb-4"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" w